  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial examines the analgesia of the fibula free flap donor site by peri-neuronal
      catheter in oro-pharyngeal carcinoma surgery by comparing continuous infusion of a local
      anesthetic with systemic multimodal analgesia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
