  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adult patients scheduled for oro-pharyngeal carcinoma surgery with reconstruction by
             fibula free flap

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Allergy to propofol or local anesthetic (ropivacaine)

          -  Severe renal or cardiac failure
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
